# ── Authority Database (Postgres direct connection) ──
# Required for:
#   1. Outbox LISTEN/NOTIFY (push-based event processing)
#   2. Authority persistence layer (policy, capability registry)
#   3. MutationGate shadow mode
#
# Use Supabase direct connection (port 5432) or pooled (port 6543).
# Get the password from: Supabase Dashboard → Project Settings → Database
#
# Direct connection:
# AUTHORITY_DATABASE_URL=postgresql://postgres:[PASSWORD]@db.qdnmuoyqpqdewepzuezp.supabase.co:5432/postgres
#
# Pooled connection (recommended for production):
# AUTHORITY_DATABASE_URL=postgresql://postgres.qdnmuoyqpqdewepzuezp:[PASSWORD]@aws-0-ap-south-1.pooler.supabase.com:5432/postgres

# ── Migration / Backfill (Neon → Supabase transition) ──
# After migrating all data from Neon to Supabase, set:
# DATABASE_URL=postgresql://postgres:[PASSWORD]@db.qdnmuoyqpqdewepzuezp.supabase.co:5432/postgres
